n terms of frame rate and number of lines of resolution. In the United States a small number of...', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=BsY5ngEACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api', '54', '2013-09', 'Ntsc, Pal, Video, Secam, Interlaced Video, 24p, 1080p, Moving Image Formats, Palplus, Moviecd, Broadcast-Safe, Smpte 292M, 576i, Pal Re', 'Video Formats');
