sthetically and aurally pleasing spaces, while avoiding problems that could be very costly, if not impossible, to solve later.', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=ktkrzNp8zCAC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', '329', '2010', 'Principles and Practice', 'Architectural Acoustics');
