 best sensor selection for any design *covers sensors from A to Z- from basic technological fundamentals, to cutting-edge info. on the latest MEMS and the hottest nanotechnology applications', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=hPPM8G4kI0wC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', '691', '2005', DEFAULT, 'Sensor Technology Handbook');
